    # game/areas/whitemarshes02helvius.rpy:276
    old "“Huh? Why wad he be?” You pay attention to his confident stance and strong voice, with its usual hint of disdain, and spot no sign of a lie. “He’s hardly ever been here. I’ve no need of wardens.” "
